### List All Available Metrics
**PowerShell:**
```powershell
oci monitoring metric list -c $C --region $REGION --namespace oci_computeagent 2>&1 |
  ConvertFrom-Json | Select-Object -ExpandProperty data |
  ForEach-Object { Write-Host "  $($_.name)" }
```

**Bash:**
```bash
oci monitoring metric list -c $C --region $REGION --namespace oci_computeagent \
  --query 'data[].name' --output table
```

**Python:**
```python
metrics = monitoring.list_metrics(C, oci.monitoring.models.ListMetricsDetails(namespace="oci_computeagent")).data
for m in sorted(set(m.name for m in metrics)):
    print(f"  {m}")
```

